text:
In JavaCC 3.2 (available from https://javacc.dev.java.net/)
packaging, jar name and starter class were changed. They are
now:
JAR:   javacc.jar (JavaCC.zip in older versions)
CLASS: javacc (COM.sun.labs.javacc.Main)
       jjtree (COM.sun.labs.jjtree.Main)
       jjdoc  (COM.sun.labs.jjdoc.JJDocMain)
creator: juraj.torok@fujitsu.sk
